{"word":"G1245 - διακαθαρίζω - diakatharízō - dee-ak-ath-ar-id'-zo - Thoroughly purge","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διακαθαρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diakatharízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ak-ath-ar-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Thoroughly purge</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விளக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to cleanse thoroughly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G2511 - καθαρίζω - katharízō - kath-ar-id'-zo/2511\">G2511</a>; to <i>cleanse perfectly</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>winnow:</i> - throughly purge.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}